import React from 'react'
import {Label,Comment } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import { IAffilie } from '../../../app/models/affilie'
import {format} from 'date-fns'
import local from 'date-fns/locale/fr'




const Notifications : React.FC<{ affilie: IAffilie }> = ({ affilie }) =>
{

    return (

     
           

<Comment.Group>
{affilie.cartes.map(carte=> 
    <Comment>
      <Comment.Avatar src='/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
      <Comment.Content>
        <Comment.Author as='a'> 
              <Label>{format(carte.dateArrive, 'EEEE d MMMM yyyy', { locale: local }) }</Label>
           </Comment.Author>
      </Comment.Content>
    </Comment>
     )}
  </Comment.Group>
     

 
    )
  
}

export default Notifications
